{"tid":2352222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（武漢肺炎）中国排除60歲以上中国人打中国疫苗","createTime":"2021-01-04T01:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T02:43:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"36258d8fc2c9d2e20a1c5bd127b59be634ce4bfb","tid":2352222,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎疫情再起，該國也已在北京、山東等地對重點人群接種武肺疫苗，但令人傻眼的是，竟然只限18至59歲人士接種，最需要優先接種疫苗的老年人卻不能接種，此外，孕婦、哺乳期婦女與高血壓、糖尿病、惡性腫瘤等慢性病患者也排除在外，官方表示須等進一步臨床實驗結果而定。中國網民獲知後急問，「疫苗安全嗎？實驗數據公開了嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://times.hinet.net/mobile/news/23177880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimes.hinet.net%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2F23177880&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=8360c2cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://times.hinet.net/mobile/news/23177880</a>"},{"pid":"308668dc63dfaed2d2d31bb44255b54b654e50c8","tid":2352222,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"殺子文化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831c952cf85692e49c00f066eb310f2f52095ea7","tid":2352222,"uid":22422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"ok留畀香港啲廢老打先"},{"pid":"5a5ac3f5d494d70ea387731dd2467176ac525a9d","tid":2352222,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"CCTVB唔係吹奏緊支那疫苗咩<br />\n點轉彎好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da216f32b281d7decc89455c5e9158eb5a231e9c","tid":2352222,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"明明老人先係高危，後生死亡率唔高，根本就唔急，而且疫苗好大可能打左仍然會有傳染能力，就算後生嘅打晒 都減低唔到老人感染機會"},{"pid":"7e34be5ac85b98e14534006ae979ba0cb2585435","tid":2352222,"uid":39316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"因為驚老弱既打完容易死撚左搞到疫苗數據好難睇"},{"pid":"e73c00b7f68a9616c830f9ed689180ccfd716276","tid":2352222,"uid